43:31.360 --> 43:33.323
Heartbreak on heartland.

43:33.343 --> 43:35.030
What? It's not like
he came to see me.

43:35.050 --> 43:37.263
Now it's up to
Georgie to put things right.

43:37.265 --> 43:38.907
It's all my fault.

43:38.927 --> 43:40.905
- We're still good, right?
- Nothing's changed.

43:40.925 --> 43:42.100
Everything's changed.

43:42.102 --> 43:43.461
An all-new heartland,

